WEBVTT

00:00.360 --> 00:01.360
Miss Wan'er

00:01.880 --> 00:03.240
Why don't you want to marry?

00:03.400 --> 00:04.760
Though I am the eldest daughter

00:05.160 --> 00:06.640
I am not of Chen Dao's branch

00:07.360 --> 00:09.000
My father was originally the Chen family head

00:09.240 --> 00:10.160
After he passed from illness

00:10.360 --> 00:11.960
Chen Dao took power

00:12.960 --> 00:13.960
Not long after

00:14.720 --> 00:16.080
My mother also passed from illness

00:16.640 --> 00:17.400
The eldest branch

00:17.880 --> 00:19.480
Only has me, a woman, left

00:20.000 --> 00:21.640
Granduncle wants me to marry out

00:22.000 --> 00:24.240
Simply to completely end the eldest branch

00:25.640 --> 00:26.720
But granduncle

00:27.280 --> 00:28.520
The more he wants me to leave

00:28.520 --> 00:30.240
The Chen family's center of power

00:30.840 --> 00:31.880
The more I refuse to go

00:32.360 --> 00:33.520
Just like Prince of Ning

00:33.720 --> 00:34.640
To Your Highness

00:35.120 --> 00:36.480
He always looks down from above

00:36.720 --> 00:38.240
Not believing a mere woman

00:38.360 --> 00:40.000
Can truly turn things upside down

00:41.640 --> 00:42.480
And I

00:43.120 --> 00:44.760
Will show him otherwise
